Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:06.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...where we investigate theories from our everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:08.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tonight's presenters are...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.87,0:00:13.31,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's Kamaitachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get right into it. Today we've brought a theory...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...regarding a type of food that everyone loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look.  Here it is:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.95,0:00:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you send the smell of curry into a meeting, the person will eat curry afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's any doubt about this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:40.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today we investigate the theory:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:47.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If you send the smell of curry into a meeting, the person will eat curry afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.55,0:00:55.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today we've brought in six comedians for a meeting before lunchtime...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:01:01.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...where we will be sending in the smell of curry from the next room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.67,0:01:05.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,If all six eat curry after the meeting, the theory has been proved correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.99,0:01:09.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Our first target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.05,0:01:12.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Abereru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:14.49,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's so bald!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.17,0:01:22.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As they start the meeting for the fake show...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.46,0:01:26.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...we begin our grand curry plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.09,0:01:31.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you smell something good?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Something smells good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells like curry, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you eat some?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: No, I didn't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.47,0:01:45.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We continued to send in the smell of curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.47,0:01:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: OK, that's it for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:52.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The meeting is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:57.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Abareru-kun is in the driver's seat as he leaves the TBS office.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:02:03.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,From here we enlist our friends at the HAL detective agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:06.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We continue the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:10.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After driving for 10 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:15.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...we arrive at Koujimachi, where Abereru-kun's next gig is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:17.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:23.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...Abereru-kun stops and stares at a parked car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:29.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On that car?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:33.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:37.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Abereru-kun's destination is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:50.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,CoCo Ichi. (A curry restaurant chain.)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:54.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With Abereru-kun we have cleared the first level.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He really went!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: We're with TBS, can we interview you for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: What did you eat just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now? I had curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Curry with spinach.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Why did you eat curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?  Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I was hungry? No?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Any other reasons?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.47,0:03:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: The smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,During the meeting..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...it smelled so delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:41.65,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So we explained today's theory to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell right into your trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:58.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:02.43,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...Viking's Nishimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:10.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Just like before, we send in the smell of curry from the room next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1070,830)}That smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: It smells good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:24.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We finish the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:29.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then Nishimura heads over to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:31.25,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:39.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Sukiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:44.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While beef on rice is their specialty, Sukiya has a diverse menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:48.89,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What did Nishimura end up eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Nishimura-san, pardon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:59.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Staff: We're with TBS.  Can we speak to you for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:04:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: What did you eat just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I had curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,CLEAR
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:12.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We explained today's theory to Nishimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it did smell like curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Would you say that influenced you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...I don't really know the answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:27.79,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Why the hell not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...I don't like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I really like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I really eat it because of the smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.23,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:43.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next we have...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:49.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Anthony from Matenrou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there a really strong curry smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I imagining that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: No, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It does, right?  It smells like curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:11.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:17.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After walking around Akasaka for five minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:26.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Anthony walks into...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...an udon restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:32.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However, if we look at the menu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:38.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...there's still a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:41.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Staff: Anthony-san, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:44.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Staff: We're from TBS.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: We want to ask you a couple of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: What did you eat just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Udon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was eating udon noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.61,0:06:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Udon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Udon...I was eating curry udon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:04.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,CLEAR
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Why did you choose curry udon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Wait, what is this? I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because the room smelled like curry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, that's probably why I chose to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, I was thinking of eating udon...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:37.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,So we explained today's theory to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, so I ate it because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like such a dweeb.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone feels like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:53.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Our next target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1020,600)}Arapon from Anzen Manzai
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That smells good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells like the curry I eat at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.41,0:08:01.03,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However, the store he entered was also an udon restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi - ohh what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Just now, what did you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now? I was eating curry udon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:21.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,CLEAR
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you would...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, would you eat it after that?  I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:29.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next, the fifth target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(250,790)}Kuro-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It really smells good, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Does it smell good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.64,0:08:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: The smell of curry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:43.43,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Kuro-chan, is it ok \Nto follow you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:54.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We also have success with Kuro-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Brunch: Veggie curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:09:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of rice, I'm eating it with veggies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Healthy! Extra veggies with a small portion of curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:09.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However, in reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:12.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...he was hiding the rice under the veggies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:16.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In fact, it was two servings of rice plus udon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.93,0:09:20.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A lie was smeared with extra carbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Lastly we have...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:32.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Noda Crystal from Magical Lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:38.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We sent in the smell of curry like we had done before, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: About five years?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Do you remember how much you were smoking in those days?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was a pack a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:49.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Unlike the others before him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:52.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...Noda doesn't mention the smell at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:58.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After the meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:03.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...he went from Akasaka to Ogikubo by train.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:07.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The restaurant Noda entered was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:18.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...a yakitori restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:21.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The theory was not proven true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't like curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In conclusion, some people don't like curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So...what did everyone think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:39.95,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's brainwashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like somehow this can be used to influence people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, backstage today...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...there was a curry lunch, and a regular lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one did you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:54.58,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,The non-curry one.
